_sText:
This is a skill surf map with 6 stages.
The stages aren't very long, but hard (at least I hope so ;)).
There are 2 jails, one of them is only available, if someone finishes the map.
If all people fail, they get teleported in the other jail (see last picture) and get weapons, depending on the stage where they failed at.
